definition: to emerge
to float/superficial/floating/unstable/movable/provisional/temporary/transient/impetuous/hollow/inflated/to exceed/superfluous/excessive/surplus

to go out/to come out/to occur/to produce/to go beyond/to rise/to put forth/to happen/(used after a verb to indicate an outward direction or a positive result)/classifier for dramas, plays, operas etc
to float up (idiom); to become evident/to surface/to appear

sentences.english: Yet there may be another supercycle emerging – that is, for gold.
sentences.chinese: 而另一場大牛市可能正在浮出水面，那就是黃金。

sentences.english: He came out from the water immediately, climbed up the bank, and made off for home at once.
sentences.chinese: 他迅速浮出水面，上岸後撒腿就往家跑。

sentences.english: Gathering them unemotionally will help those facts come out.
sentences.chinese: 非情緒化地收集事實會幫助那些事實浮出水面。

sentences.english: Ron Artest doesn't read - he stares down books until they give up the information.
sentences.chinese: 阿泰不閱讀，他盯着書，直到他們浮出字爲止。

sentences.english: The new sorting device of floating roller is designed.
sentences.chinese: 設計了新型輥子浮出式貨物分類裝置。

sentences.english: Time has finished reading right away having spent three section of class's like this "float out sea surface ".
sentences.chinese: 就這麼花了三節課的時間讀完了《浮出海面》。

sentences.english: Liu brought the transgender issue to the surface.
sentences.chinese: 劉著讓跨性別問題浮出水面。

sentences.english: It emerged about a hundred years after production became mechanized.
sentences.chinese: 一百年後生產機械化後品牌才浮出水面。

sentences.english: The next revolution has not yet surfaced.
sentences.chinese: 下一場革命還沒有浮出水面。

sentences.english: Another bit of evidence for Apple's world view emerged this week.
sentences.chinese: 蘋果公司的世界觀的另一個證據本週浮出水面。

sentences.english: The deal emerged late on Saturday after fractious public exchanges earlier in the day between Republicans and Democrats.
sentences.chinese: 在週六共和黨和民主黨惡語相向以後，協議浮出水面。

sentences.english: In a world of big data the correlations surface almost by themselves.
sentences.chinese: 在龐大數據的世界中，相關數據幾乎是自行浮出水面。

sentences.english: This IP address lets big Peng press down Zhu Mou to rise to surface.
sentences.chinese: 這個IP地址讓大彭鎮褚某浮出水面。

sentences.english: This is coming to a head in November.
Jen-Huey Chiang and his family began to emerge of the dust-laden history.
sentences.chinese: 姜仁惠及其家族的塵封歷史開始浮出水面。

sentences.english: They waited for over a month, but the huge turtle did not appear on the sea.
sentences.chinese: 可是，它們等了一個多月，大鰲還沒浮出海面。
